{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Home - My Professional Portfolio{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <section class="hero-section">
        <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">Welcome to my Portfolio</h1>
        
        <div class="bio-content">
            <p class="description">
                Currently a student in Computer Science, I am a passionate developer who specializes in building robust and modern web applications. 
                My journey into the world of technology began during my <strong>STI2D parcour in High School</strong>, where I developed a strong interest in programming logic, digital systems, and innovative solutions.
            </p>

            <p class="description">
                This initial experience was a true turning point. Since then, I have been constantly expanding my technical stack, with a primary focus on <strong>Cisco Packet Tracer and learning Cybersecurity</strong>. 
                I enjoy solving complex problems, optimizing code performance, and creating great user experiences.
            </p>

            <h2 style="color: #00d4ff; margin-top: 30px;">Technical Skills</h2>
            <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; gap: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
